description: The fund, under normal market conditions, will invest primarily in equity securities, including exchange-traded common stocks, exchange-traded preferred stocks and exchange-traded real estate investment trusts ("REITs"). Typically, its portfolio will generally hold 20 to 40 securities. The fund may invest in companies with any market capitalization, although, it will typically focus its investments in mid- to large- capitalization companies. It is non-diversified.
name: Natixis Vaughan Nelson Select ETF
